{"title": "Future Developments", "body": {"ops": [{"attributes": {"color": "#50c75a", "underline": true}, "insert": "Future Developments"}, {"attributes": {"header": 2}, "insert": "\n"}, {"insert": "Despite that, we must acknowledge features missing from the "}, {"attributes": {"color": "#52cca3"}, "insert": "final design"}, {"insert": ". In particular, we missed out on implementing:\n\n"}, {"attributes": {"color": "#50c75a"}, "insert": "Localisation"}, {"insert": ": The final app was only"}, {"attributes": {"color": "#52cca3"}, "insert": " localised to English"}, {"insert": ", and so was not as accessible as it could have been. Especially, support for "}, {"attributes": {"color": "#52cca3"}, "insert": "non-Latin characters"}, {"insert": " was not extensive."}, {"attributes": {"list": "bullet"}, "insert": "\n"}, {"insert": "\n"}, {"attributes": {"color": "#50c75a"}, "insert": "Collaborative notes"}, {"insert": ": "}, {"attributes": {"color": "#52cca3"}, "insert": "Multiple users"}, {"insert": " cannot edit notes in an "}, {"attributes": {"color": "#52cca3"}, "insert": "on-line fashion"}, {"insert": ", which limits the usability of the app in group settings."}, {"attributes": {"color": "#52cca3"}, "insert": " Despite this"}, {"insert": ", notes can be "}, {"attributes": {"color": "#52cca3"}, "insert": "shared very easily"}, {"insert": ", simply by"}, {"attributes": {"color": "#52cca3"}, "insert": " copy-and-pasting "}, {"insert": "note files between devices."}, {"attributes": {"list": "bullet"}, "insert": "\n"}, {"insert": "\n"}, {"attributes": {"color": "#50c75a"}, "insert": "A more complex note management system"}, {"insert": ": Currently, notes are all stored in a "}, {"attributes": {"color": "#52cca3"}, "insert": "flat file"}, {"insert": ". In future, a "}, {"attributes": {"color": "#52cca3"}, "insert": "directory system"}, {"insert": " for the user to "}, {"attributes": {"color": "#52cca3"}, "insert": "group shared notes together"}, {"insert": ", or perhaps even something more "}, {"attributes": {"color": "#52cca3"}, "insert": "complex"}, {"insert": ", would be a great boon to the "}, {"attributes": {"color": "#52cca3"}, "insert": "usability "}, {"insert": "of the app."}, {"attributes": {"list": "bullet"}, "insert": "\n"}, {"insert": "\nIn spite of the above, it must be noted that the"}, {"attributes": {"color": "#52cca3"}, "insert": " modularity of the design"}, {"insert": " allows users to"}, {"attributes": {"color": "#52cca3"}, "insert": " add these features in themselves"}, {"insert": "!\n\n"}, {"attributes": {"link": "#pres_4"}, "insert": "previous slide"}, {"insert": " | "}, {"attributes": {"link": "#pres_6"}, "insert": "next slide"}, {"attributes": {"align": "center"}, "insert": "\n"}, {"attributes": {"header": 2}, "insert": "\n"}]}, "text": "Future Developments\n\nDespite that, we must acknowledge features missing from the final design. In particular, we missed out on implementing:\n\n\n\n\nLocalisation: The final app was only localised to English, and so was not as accessible as it could have been. Especially, support for non-Latin characters was not extensive.\n\n\n\n\nCollaborative notes: Multiple users cannot edit notes in an on-line fashion, which limits the usability of the app in group settings. Despite this, notes can be shared very easily, simply by copy-and-pasting note files between devices.\n\n\n\n\nA more complex note management system: Currently, notes are all stored in a flat file. In future, a directory system for the user to group shared notes together, or perhaps even something more complex, would be a great boon to the usability of the app.\n\n\n\n\nIn spite of the above, it must be noted that the modularity of the design allows users to add these features in themselves!\n\n\n\n\nprevious slide | next slide\n\n\n", "updatedAt": 1714677671987}